            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#898989' fontsize='8'>-Most customers are low-value, indicating low engagement and repeat purchases. </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#898989' fontsize='8'>-With very few high-value customers, revenue is at risk, but medium-value customers present a strong growth opportunity.</run>
